WEBVTT

00:02.410 --> 00:04.900
I guess it sounds like I’m bad-mouthing her.

00:04.900 --> 00:08.250
There are some strange things about Lain, but she’s an ordinary girl.

00:08.740 --> 00:12.280
She could be much attractive and popular if she would lighten up.

00:12.560 --> 00:13.660
She’s gentle, too.

00:13.660 --> 00:14.720
Gentle.

00:14.720 --> 00:17.370
So what subjects do you tutor?

00:18.570 --> 00:19.650
All subjects.

00:19.890 --> 00:20.940
Wow, I’m jealous.

00:20.950 --> 00:24.660
I’m no good at all at math.

00:24.670 --> 00:26.880
Lain’s grades are perfect.

00:26.880 --> 00:29.620
I wish I had a private tutor.
